TY  - JOUR
T1  - Efficient Use of Information and Social Value of Information
AU  - Angeletos, George-Marios
AU  - Pavan, Alessandro
Y1  - 2007/07/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/07/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-0262.2007.00783.x
T2  - Econometrica
