TY  - JOUR
T1  - Nonparametric Matching and Efficient Estimators of Homothetically Separable Functions
AU  - Lewbel, Arthur
AU  - Linton, Oliver
Y1  - 2007/07/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/07/01
